## Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| VK from WASM has unexpected length (not 896 or 897) | Low | Medium вҖ” keygen fails | `deserializePublicKeyNtt` handles both lengths and gives clear error message |
| `bitBuffer` overflow with `\|=` and `<<` in JavaScript | Low | High вҖ” silent data corruption | Use `>>>` (unsigned right shift) instead of `>>`, bit buffer stays within 32-bit safe range (max 22 bits in buffer at any time) |
| Mock `fill(2)` bytes produce coefficients >= Q | Very Low | Medium вҖ” existing tests break | Verified by calculation: repeating 0x02 decodes to [514, 2056, 8224, 128] cycle, all < 12289 |
| `serializePublicKeyNtt` test helper has bugs that mask deserialization bugs | Low | High вҖ” false-positive tests | Added independent tests: all-zeros, max-valid, raw byte corruption with 0xFF |

